Class TimeSlot

java.lang.Object
model.appointments.TimeSlot
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<TimeSlot>
public class TimeSlot extends Object implements Serializable, Comparable<TimeSlot>
An immutable representation of a time slot for appointments, encapsulating a specific LocalDateTime.
